==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lustering
<hw>Lus"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or process
of imparting a luster, as to pottery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The brightening of a metal in the crucible when it
becomes pure, as in certain refining processes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lustreless</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Lusterless</ent>⟦br⟧
